citations:
    citation-agot-jon-iii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Jon III"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Jon Snow trains Night's Watch recruits under Ser Alliser Thorne at Castle Black. Introduces Grenn (called 'the Aurochs'), Halder, Jeren, Toad, Pyp (Pypar), Rast. Tyrion Lannister visits the Wall and gives Jon his famous quote about bastards and broken things. Jon tells Tyrion he plans to search for his uncle Benjen if Benjen doesn't return. Ghost (Jon's direwolf) is present."
